snippet.title: Bugsnax: The Isle of BIGsnax FREE Content Update Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: In the Isle of BIGsnax FREE content update, explore a mysterious new land crawling with supersized Bugsnax. Back on Snaktooth, you can complete challenges from your mailbox, collect decorations to personalize your hut, and most important of all: put hats on your favorite Bugsnax! This free content update to Bugsnax will be available early 2022 on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Epic Games Store, and Steam.
